ėHAROLD ARTHUR DUDMAN:
MARCH 5TH 1923 - JUNE 6TH 2009
FREEMAN OF THE CITY OF LONDON,
WANDSMAN OF
ST. PAUL'S CATHEDRAL

[Second inscription added 2019]
ALSO HIS BELOVED WIFE
OF 58 YEARS
EDITH IRENE (LESLEY) DUDMAN
JANUARY 26TH 1926 - MARCH 24TH 2019
REUNITED FOR ETERNITY"°
ěDedicated to the memory of
Rene Tkacik
who lost his life working in the Crossrail tunnels
on the 7th of March 2014
from his family, friends and colleagues"§
°MATT SKELTON
(13 Oct 1966 - 27 July 2009)
An inspiring teacher, a wise colleague,
a splendid companion, a keen gardener,
remembered fondly and gratefully by all."•
