űTo remember with great love
Diana Constance Simmonds
(1929-2017) (Mum, Gran, Di-Di)
The most wonderful and loyal mother, grandmother, friend and neighbour
She lived in Holborn for most of her life and loved this square. "I know we'll meet again""ķ
